@page "/about"

<div class="container my-5">
    <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-8 text-4xl font-bold text-center">About Me</h2>
    <div class="bg-white p-4 shadow-sm rounded-lg mb-6">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
            I'm a seasoned .NET developer with a strong foundation in software engineering and cloud technologies.
            My journey in technology began with my undergraduate studies, and has since evolved through various
            roles and educational pursuits.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
            Today, I specialize in .NET development with practical experience in React and Azure cloud services.
            I'm passionate about creating efficient, scalable solutions that solve real-world problems.
        </p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-8 text-4xl font-bold text-center">Education</h2>
    <div class="timeline relative">
        <!-- Line down the middle -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-0.5 bg-gray-200"></div>

        <!-- Masters Degree -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
            <div class="transform translate-x-1/2 md:translate-x-0 md:ml-[50%] md:pl-8 relative">
                <!-- Timeline dot -->
                <div
                    class="absolute top-5 -left-3 md:-left-[17px] w-6 h-6 bg-gray-700 rounded-full border-4 border-white">
                </div>
                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="bg-white p-4 shadow-sm rounded-lg ml-4 md:ml-0">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">M.Tech Computer Network & Engineering</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500">Manipal Intitute of Technology, Manipal</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-gray-500">2016 - 2018</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        During my masters program, I expanded my theoretical knowledge and practical skills in computer
                        networking and engineering.
                        This academic pursuit has proved invaluable in my professional growth, providing me with
                        advanced understanding of software architecture, algorithms, and system design.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bachelors Degree -->
        <div class="relative">
            <div class="transform -translate-x-1/2 md:translate-x-0 md:mr-[50%] md:pr-8 relative">
                <!-- Timeline dot -->
                <div
                    class="absolute top-5 right-[-27px] md:right-[-11px] w-6 h-6 bg-gray-700 rounded-full border-4 border-white">
                </div>
                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="bg-white p-4 shadow-sm rounded-lg mr-4 md:mr-0">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">B.E Computer Science</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500"> Sahyadri College of Engineering & Management, Mangalore</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-gray-500"> 2010 - 2014</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Completed my undergraduate studies with a focus on computer science and software engineering,
                        establishing a strong foundation in programming and software development principles.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

